The Basketball Scoreboard app allows you to keep track of scores for both the home and guest team.
It allows you to increment the scores by values of 1, 2, and 3
You can clear the scoreboard
A Timer can be set by using the START/RESET TIMER button
And you can reset the timer whenever you want to.
At the end of the game. The timer disappears and "FINAL TIME" message appears.
It also then displays a result of what team beat who, and by the goal difference or whether they drew
